title: Welcome to 2 bathroom house is located in Irving
posting_body: Welcome to 2 bathroom house is located in Irving, and boasts beautiful 9ft ceilings, laminate and Lino flooring, newer finishing's throughout and air conditioning for those hot summer days!
Finished basement has additional room and full bathroom with a tub, along with laundry.
The private backyard is fenced and has a large, 2-car detached heated garage available for parking and storage.
Close to many amenities such as downtown, Was Cana Lake, schools, tennis courts, and parks.
